editorialNotes.standard: When we want to hunker down and type without distraction, one of our favorite resources is iA Writer. Plus, a streamlined interface lets you simply swipe left to preview a document and swipe right to access your library. The entire experience is designed to be quick and easy so you can focus on your work.
